I"k<h3 id="about-me">About me</h3>

<p>I am a PhD candidate at the <a href="http://crest.science/">Center for Research in Economics and Statistics (CREST)</a>. My supervisor is <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/alessandroriboni/">Alessandro Riboni</a>.</p>

<p>I study topics related to political economy, law, and crime. I’m also interested in econometrics and machine learning.</p>

<p>I am currently visiting ETH Zürich, invited by <a href="https://elliottash.com/">Elliott Ash</a>.</p>

<p>I am also a doctoral affiliate at the <a href="https://www.ipp.eu/">Institute for Public Policies (IPP)</a>.</p>

